AYDRIAN AND AEVETARE <br>
<br>
Montag and I were deep inside Blackburrow when I received a message from Merani.  <br>
<br>
        “Are you going to be in Blackburrow for a while?”<br>
        “For a while, yes.  Why?”<br>
        “Stay there.  We’re on our way.”<br>
<br>
Merani was finally returning to Qeynos!  This was big news!  I would finally meet my mentor and idol face to face.  When she arrived, was I disappointed?  Heaven’s no.<br>
<br>
Merani was beautiful, wearing exotic armor and strange weapons, the powers of which were, to me, a mystery.  She was the definition of style and grace, and yet with a fierce energy!  What a lady!  <br>
<br>
She was not alone.  At her side was a fellow named Aydrian a half elf Warrior, dressed from head to toe in shiny silver armor.  He was a small fellow, not particularly impressive in bulk.   But the skinny exterior was deceiving.  This guy could wield a two-hander like nobody!  Merani and Aydrian were cute together, an awesome twosome, and he doted on her continuously, massaging her shoulders, calling her sweetie, etc.  It wasn’t a big surprise someone had snatched Merani up and called dibbs. <br>
<br>
Montag emerged and was introduced to Ayd and Merani as well.  I quietly asked Merani what had been on my mind for some time.<br>
<br>
        “Can Montag be in the guild too?”  <br>
<br>
Merani was going to be selective.  There were no free rides around THIS gal.  “Tell me about him,” she said.  <br>
<br>
I plead his case.  I can’t remember what that case was, but I know how I ended it.  “Look,” I said, &quot;he’s saved my neck more times than I can count.”  <br>
<br>
Whatever I said, she liked it.  Montag was in.<br>
<br>
As I recall, Merani was not feeling well and retired quickly after.  Someone else arrived, and Aydrian spoke with this fellow at length.  I heard their conversation, but it was filled with jargon I could not understand, much less remember.  What WAS clear was that these two had bonded in the trenches of battle and there was a deep respect between them.  I'm almost certain that this new fellow met Montag as well for the first time in that moment.  This fellow's name was Aevetare.  <br>
<br>
Next to Ayd, Aevetare was immense, not at all gangly like Aydrian.  Aeve was short on words and sentiment.  The strong silent type.  After conversing for some time, Aeve handed me a gift. <br>
<br>
The item was the single greatest weapon I had ever seen, a two-hand slash Shiny Brass Halberd!  Now, by today’s standards, this Halberd was junk, but back then, it was an awesome magic item for a young Ranger to wield.  I fell to bended knee and thanked Aevetare for this gift.  Wow!!<br>
<br>
Aydrian took me deep into Blackburrow, to places Montag and I wouldn’t DARE enter.  He pulled, I fought for a few licks, and then Ayd killed the gnoll.  But it was I who got the experience.  And I was hitting INCREDIBLE damage with my new weapon.<br>
<br>
        “That’s a good weapon for you,” said Aevetare, who I then realized was in the shadows nearby.  He gave me a massive heal and my wounds disappeared. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub66.ezboard.com/bthearrowoflightcommons.showUserPublicProfile?gid=sytox>Sytox</A> at: 1/18/03 1:53:07 am<br></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub66.ezboard.com/fthearrowoflightcommonsfrm23.showPrevMessage?topicID=4.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub66.ezboard.com/fthearrowoflightcommonsfrm23.showNextMessage?topicID=4.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub66.ezboard.com/fthearrowoflightcommonsfrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4.topic><img src=http://www.eq-arrow-of-light.com/aol/images/boardbuttons/reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub66.ezboard.com/fthearrowoflightcommonsfrm23.emailToFriend?topicID=4.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub66.ezboard.com/fthearrowoflightcommonsfrm23.threadControl?topicID=4.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub66.ezboard.com/fthearrowoflightcommonsfrm23.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=4.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub66.ezboard.com/fthearrowoflightcommonsfrm23.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=4.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to s